{"id":3058,"date":"2025-05-17T10:06:20","date_gmt":"2025-05-17T03:06:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=3058"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:37:26","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:37:26","slug":"mun-nhan-viem-nhe","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/mun-nhan-viem-nhe\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ee5n nh\u00e2n vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho m\u1ee5n nh\u00e2n, vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9 v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nhanh c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ch\u1ebft.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho da m\u1ee5n.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf g\u00e2y ra s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7, s\u1eb9o x\u1ea5u.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u1ee5n tr\u00ean da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n chu\u1ea9n y khoa.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1i vi\u00eam sau li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng n\u1ec1n, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da sau n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da tinh ch\u1ea5t m\u1ee5n &amp; kem ch\u1ea5p m\u1ee5n GSC t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da sau x\u1ea5m l\u1ea5n GSC Ultra Calming K Cream v\u1edbi VITAMIN K, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t c\u00fac la m\u00e3 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 2 ti\u1ebfng.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 \u2013 05 l\u1ea7n, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -16px; top: 368.259px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho m\u1ee5n nh\u00e2n, vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9 v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3636,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[36],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-3058","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-mun","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3058","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3058"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3636"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3058"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=3058"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=3058"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=3058"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}